{"tid":955913,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"黑暗童話 - 神的設計","createTime":"2018-12-25T20:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T05:51:15.000Z","uid":171572,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88dc2d387cf133d5b211561ce930d1d61ebe9ba6","tid":955913,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T20:54:07.000Z","msg":"從前神創造了一男一女。神賦予了男人性慾，但是卻沒有把這種慾望賦予給女人。<br />\n<br />\n有一天，男人和女人相遇了。男人天天求愛，但都被女人拒絕。男人覺得這麽做很煩人，是強人所難。男人很苦惱，他跑去見神。<br />\n<br />\n男人問道：我的神呀。我很想愛愛，而女人不願意，那該怎麽辦好？<br />\n<br />\n神道：除了你們，我還創造了一群鴨子。你有吃鴨子的慾望，但鴨子卻不想被吃，你怎麽辦？最後你不還是吃了。這就是為甚我設計了人類強大於鴨子，而且男人強大於女人。我為你設計了這麽一條道路。<br />\n<br />\n男人回答道：嘿，我懂了。感謝神，我先退下了。<br />\n<br />\n神看了一下男人的背影，嘆了一個氣，抬起手一揮，就把男人和女人的靈魂交換了。"},{"pid":"5535165b2698a76a919ac3b498f44d536a13c716","tid":955913,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a8158f189b8ec9955af0481c6f245d1284624b","tid":955913,"uid":157204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T22:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf00997d1d61f3061dc6065b9e306d6492c5021","tid":955913,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T22:42:13.000Z","msg":"呢個故既背景一定係香港 影射港男<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045d42aef8dd3f0f5ffc87fcf6437bbc609742c","tid":955913,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"到底男人嘿啲咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc95ad667383ed7c5817d1b24f0f943995ab4c8a","tid":955913,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5045d42aef8dd3f0f5ffc87fcf6437bbc609742c","tid":955913,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"到底男人嘿啲咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}